  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Software/firmware update events for electronic devices (OTA security patch and manual BIOS update).",
    "softwareUpdateEvent is the actual observation (what changed in this event) and stays at event level.",
    "softwareSupport describes the product's resulting current support state (OS, firmware, latest update",
    "date) and lives inside masterDataAvailableFor on the product entry; it's master data, not an",
    "event observation.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,euelec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/electronics/",
    "See: core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
